MASTER PROTECTION
- Protected branches: master
- Required status checks: travic CI passing build
- Required reviews / approval

MY WORKFLOW
$ script-scaffold-module ^
$ script-split
    $ $EDITOR
    $ npm test:watch
^ PUBLISH

